## POST /utils/events/is-modifier-match

### Description
Matches a KeyboardEvent against an expected modifier state.

### Method
POST

### Endpoint
/utils/events/is-modifier-match

### Parameters
#### Request Body
- **event** (`KeyboardEventModifiers`) - Required - A KeyboardEvent or structurally similar object.
