{
  "matches": true
}
```

## POST /utils/events/is-exact-shortcut-match

### Description
Performs an exact match of a KeyboardEvent against a specific key and modifier state.

### Method
POST

### Endpoint
/utils/events/is-exact-shortcut-match

### Parameters
